{"title":"幼林（外一首）","authors":["李清联"],"dates":[{"year":1983,"month":5,"day":24}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"幼林（外一首）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"李清联"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这么多绿娃娃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这么多绿娃娃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在阳光下唱，春风里舞。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我来到这里就陶醉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"感到一种作父亲的满足："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的幼林多么茁壮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正由稚嫩跨向成熟。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我多想抚摸这些娃娃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"却够不着它们的头，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只好扶住它们可爱的枝丫，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摸了又摸，抚了又抚。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"娃娃们却借助风在唱："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳光、理想、幸福……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我深深思索我们的绿化，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎会有丰富的叶绿素？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不是泥土比昨天肥沃，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也并非气候比昨天湿润，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雨量比昨天充足……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我为山的今天祝福吧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它不再姓“荒”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也不再姓“秃”；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让我也为山的明天祝福吧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它是采伐梁柱的林场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓄积兵械的武库。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"储木场"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"集栋梁之材于储木场，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"待运整装——儿女志在四方。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生在伏牛的栋梁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长在伏牛的栋梁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它木质的馨香，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也带着泥土的芬芳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伏牛山——木材之乡，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"汽车驮载火车装，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"原始老林没采完，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新林日夜刷刷长！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"瞧那青松紫椴茁壮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是伏牛的小伙；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看那赤桦白桦向上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象伏牛的姑娘。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今日出山忙，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"告别伏牛亲爹娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎不见凄凄别情泪两行，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没一点儿惆怅？！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"何惆怅？！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"伏牛儿女心胸多坦荡。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在山——把天下惦心上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"出山——也是为了家乡……"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}